data.title: Harry HUGHES
data.text:
Notes for Harry & Jennie Jeanette (Family)

Returns of marriage for County of Livingston, State of Missouri record 35, date of licence Mar 29 1916 Harry Hughes age 25 of Brighton, Michigan born Lancashire, England, farmer, father Thos. Hughes and mother Anna Dixon and Jennie J Duckering age 28 of Brighton, Michigan born Brighton, Michigan at home, father John Duckering and mother Emily Fall married Mar 30 1916 Brighton, Michigan by H A Blake Pastor and witnessed by Mr & Mrs Bidwell both of Brighton, Michigan - see copy
